{"tid":1094640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角砵蘭街女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-04-06T12:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T13:52:57.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14f15c658b2da29b52bac6589cceda9fee44edf8","tid":1094640,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"旺角砵蘭街136號一幢唐樓，今日（6日）下午5時許，一名30餘歲女子突然由上址天台高處墮下，砸毀一部冷氣機，並倒臥在毗鄰138號大廈的簷篷上重傷，途人發現報案。消防員趕至利用雲梯，將事主抬落地面，經救護員檢驗後，證實事主已死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方用帳篷將其遺體遮蓋，並在天台發現事主的鞋及手袋，經初步調查後，相信事件沒有可疑，正聯絡事主的家人助查，以了解事主尋死原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=2e207b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/bkn-20190406174229278-0406_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190406%2Fbkn-20190406174229278-0406_00822_001.html&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=a2642a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190406/bkn-20190406174229278-0406_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6674a19d5e2fddc1e8acf626571d386d63450d99","tid":1094640,"uid":113626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔明香港點樣係一個成功地區"},{"pid":"02392ee1294b55b4d478542259a41e024ca41394","tid":1094640,"uid":125978,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"其實都已經2019年啦，仲玩自殺，會唔會out左啲。"},{"pid":"590f8ed3c5f2fe73d285c547b9e0a4c948a51fcb","tid":1094640,"uid":85461,"l